et ingredients, mixing on low speed until just combined. Do not overmix.\n6. **Fold in chocolate chips:** Stir in the chocolate chips with a spatula or wooden spoon.\n7. **Scoop the dough:** Drop rounded tablespoons of dough onto the prepared baking sheets, spacing them about 2 inches apart.\n8. **Bake:** Bake for 9–11 minutes, or until the edges are golden brown but the centers still look slightly underdone.\n9. **Cool:** Let the cookies cool on the baking sheet for 5 minutes, then transfer to a wire rack to cool completely.\n\n## Tips\n\n- **Chill the dough** for at least 30 minutes before baking for thicker, chewier cookies.\n- **Use room-temperature eggs** for a smoother batter.\n- **Don't overbake!** The cookies will continue to firm up as they cool.\n\n## Yield\n\nMakes approximately **4 dozen** cookies.\n\nEnjoy! 🍪"},"providerExecuted":false,"options":{}}],"options":{}},{"role":"tool","content":[{"type":"tool-result","id":"toolu_014SmRh441jNDzHXWkaPxy2B","name":"create","isFailure":false,"result":{"_id":"Exit","_tag":"Success","value":{"id":"dxn:echo:BDJXMULPW5FB55UZ7KP5HLDHVTXUTHE2U:01JGFJJZ00G0WKQSJGMAKCNTJ0"}},"providerExecuted":false,"options":{}}],"options":{"anthropic":{"cacheControl":{"ttl":"5m","type":"ephemeral"}}}}]},"response":[{"type":"response-metadata","id":"msg_01VGzZHr5BVDiVjWvGRr5KSg","modelId":"claude-opus-4-6","timestamp":"2026-05-14T15:28:02.265Z","metadata":{}},{"type":"reasoning-start","id":"0","metadata":{}},{"type":"reasoning-delta","id":"0","delta":"The","metadata":{}},{"type":"reasoning-delta","id":"0","delta":" document was created successfully.","metadata":{}},{"type":"reasoning-delta","id":"0","delta":"","metadata":{"anthropic":{"type":"thinking","signature":""}}},{"type":"reasoning-end","id":"0","metadata":{}},{"type":"text-start","id":"1","metadata":{}},{"type":"text-delta","id":"1","delta":"Your cookie recipe document has been created! 🍪 It includes","metadata":{}},{"type":"text-delta","id":"1","delta":":\n\n- **Title:** Classi